<!--簡介與症狀-->
'''天花'''（{{lang-en|Smallpox}}）是一種由[[天花病毒|天花病毒]]引起之人類[[傳染病|傳染病]]。患者一般在染病後的12天內，出現包括[[發燒|發燒]]、[[肌肉疼痛|肌肉疼痛]]、[[頭痛|頭痛]]等近似[[普通感冒|普通感冒]]的[[症狀|症狀]]。幾天後，[[口|口]][[咽|咽]]部分的[[粘膜|粘膜]]會長出紅點，身體多處地方亦會長出皮疹（以臉部居多）。<ref name=eMedicine_Smallpox/>天花病毒共有兩類：主天花病毒及次天花病毒。根據患者的病情發展，由前者引發之天花又被劃分為四種形式：典型、惡性、出血型、緩和型。其中，多數未曾接種疫苗者均會出現典型天花的症狀。<ref name= PinkBook/>次天花病毒引起之病變程度比上述四種都要溫和，但卻非常罕見。<ref name=FactSheet/>

<!--病源與預防方法-->
天花主要透過[[空氣傳播疾病|空氣傳播]]。患者的[[呼吸道|呼吸道]]與皮膚皰疹分泌物均載有病毒，故避免與其近距離接觸可減低患病的風險。<ref name=AFIP/>多種[[痘病毒|痘病毒]]疾病的[[醫學徵象|病癥]]均與天花的如出一轍。專家需利用{{link-en|絨毛尿囊膜|Chorioallantoic membrane}}進行[[病毒培養|病毒培植]]以確定天花病毒的存在，[[聚合酶鏈式反應|聚合酶鏈式反應]]及[[限制性片段長度多態性|限制性片段長度多態性]]測試可提供更多病毒的細節。<ref name=diagnosis1/><ref name=diagnosis2/>接種[[天花疫苗|天花疫苗]]為預防此病的最佳方法。<ref name=CDCvac/>目前並沒有認可的抗天花藥物。一旦出現確診病例，醫護人員會為病人注射疫苗提升免疫保護，有時亦會配以舒緩性療法加大療效。<ref name=CDCvac/>天花病毒不會造成慢性或復發性感染，但會導致各類[[併發症|併發症]]或後遺症（如[[失明|失明]]）。<ref name=AFIP/>不同類型的天花所引發的[[病死率|病死率]]不一；最為常見的典型天花約奪取了三成病患者的性命。<ref name=training1/><ref name=USAMRIID>{{Cite journal|url = http://www.usamriid.army.mil/education/bluebookpdf/USAMRIID%20BlueBook%207th%20Edition%20-%20Sep%202011.pdf|title = USAMRIID's Medical Management of Biological Casualties Handbook|last = USAMRIID|first = |date = 2011|journal = |accessdate = |doi = |pmid = |isbn = 9780160900150|edition = 7th|publisher = U.S. Government Printing Office|archive-date = 2015-02-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150209044622/http://www.usamriid.army.mil/education/bluebookpdf/USAMRIID%20BlueBook%207th%20Edition%20-%20Sep%202011.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref>

<!--疾病歷史-->
[[古埃及|古埃及]]或許為天花的起源地。已死去逾三千年的[[法老|法老]][[拉美西斯五世|拉美西斯五世]]可能是史上已知最早的天花病人，專家在其[[木乃伊|木乃伊]]身上找到了明顯的膿皰痕跡。<ref name=Ramses>{{cite web|last=Hopkins|first=Donald|title=Ramses V: Earliest known victim?|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/smallpox/WH_5_1980_p22.pdf|publisher=[[世界衛生組織|World Health Organization]]|date=1980|accessdate=2015-10-03|archive-date=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120706233352/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/smallpox/WH_5_1980_p22.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>早期的[[印度|印度]]及[[古中國|中國]]文獻亦有記載這種疾病。<ref name=Hopkins_2002>{{cite book | author = Hopkins DR | title = The Greatest Killer: Smallpox in history | edition = | publisher = [[芝加哥大學出版社|''University of Chicago Press'']]| isbn = 0-226-35168-8 |date=2002}}</ref>在隨後的漫長歲月裡，天花於世界多個地方展開大流行，並奪取了無數人類的性命（尤其是兒童）。<ref name=Hays>{{cite book |author=J. N. Hays |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=GyE8Qt-kS1kC&pg=PA151&dq=&lr=&hl=en&cd=23#v=onepage&q=false |title=Epidemics and pandemics: their impacts on human history |publisher=ABC-CLIO |page=151 |ISBN=1-85109-658-2 |date=2005 |access-date=2015-03-10 |archive-date=2014-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010084524/http://books.google.com/books?id=GyE8Qt-kS1kC&pg=PA151&dq=&lr=&hl=en&cd=23#v=onepage&q=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Behbehani_1983>{{cite journal |author=Behbehani AM |title=The smallpox story: life and death of an old disease. |journal=Microbiol Rev |volume=47 |issue=4 |pages=455–509 |date=1983-01-12 |pmid=6319980 |pmc=281588 |url=http://mmbr.asm.org/content/47/4/455.long |accessdate=2015-10-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170201235848/http://mmbr.asm.org/content/47/4/455.long |archivedate=2017-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Riedel S |title=Edward Jenner and the history of smallpox and vaccination |pmc=1200696 |journal=Proc (Bayl Univ Med Cent) |volume=18 |issue=1 |pages=21–5 |pmid=16200144 |date=2005}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author=Koplow, David A. |title=Smallpox: the fight to eradicate a global scourge |url=http://books.google.com/books/ucpress?vid=ISBN9780520242203 |publisher=[[加州大學出版社|''University of California Press'']] |location=Berkeley |pages= |ISBN=0-520-24220-3 |date=2003 |access-date=2015-03-10 |archive-date=2015-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331192207/http://books.google.com/books/ucpress?vid=ISBN9780520242203 |dead-url=no }}</ref>歷史上，有不少國家的君王及著名人物均染上過天花。19至20世紀期間，多番的防疫行動減低了此病對群眾的威脅。最終，[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]於1980年正式宣布撲滅天花<ref name=WHO_Factsheet>{{cite web |title=Smallpox |work=WHO Factsheet |url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/smallpox/en/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070921235036/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/smallpox/en/ |archivedate=2007-09-21 |deadurl=yes |access-date=2010-05-15 }}</ref>，使之成為首個於世上絕跡的人類傳染病<ref>{{cite journal | title = (Book Review) The Eradication of Smallpox: Edward Jenner and The First and Only Eradication of a Human Infectious Disease | url = http://www.nature.com/nm/journal/v7/n1/full/nm0101_15b.html | journal = Nature Medicine | volume = 7 | pages = 15–6 | doi = 10.1038/83283 | pmid =  | last1 = De Cock | first1 = Kevin M. | issue = 1 | date = 2001 | access-date = 2015-03-10 | archive-date = 2011-09-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110919222122/http://www.nature.com/nm/journal/v7/n1/full/nm0101_15b.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Tognotti E. |title=The eradication of smallpox, a success story for modern medicine and public health: What lessons for the future? |journal=J Infect Dev Ctries |volume=4 |issue=5 |pages=264–266 |date=2010-06 |pmid=20539058 |format=PDF |doi=10.3855/jidc.1204 |url=http://www.jidc.org/index.php/journal/article/view/1204/386 |deadurl=yes |access-date=2015-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402163650/http://www.jidc.org/index.php/journal/article/view/1204/386 |archive-date=2015-04-02 }}</ref>。

==臨床分類==
天花主要有兩種臨床表現形式。常見的主天花病毒（{{lang|la|''Variola major''}}）會引發較為嚴重的[[醫學徵象|病癥]]：病人身體各部位均會長出皮疹，[[發燒|發燒]]的程度亦較為嚴重。反之，由次天花病毒（{{lang|la|''Variola minor''}}）所引起的症狀則較為溫和但罕見。<ref name=FactSheet>{{cite web |url=http://www.bt.cdc.gov/agent/smallpox/overview/disease-facts.asp |title=CDC Smallpox |accessdate=2016-06-19 |work=Smallpox Overview |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130402220850/http://www.bt.cdc.gov/agent/smallpox/overview/disease-facts.asp |archivedate=2013-04-02 }}</ref>某些曾接種疫苗的患者只發燒而不長出皮疹，此乃另一種臨床表現形式，被稱之為“無疹天花（{{lang|la|''Variola sine eruptione''}}）”。鉴定这种天花的方法有:抗体法和病毒分离法，但是后者罕为使用。<ref name = PinkBook>{{cite book
