===生物武器===
不少國家曾考慮在戰爭中使用天花作為[[生物武器|生物武器]]。1754-1763年的[[北美殖民地戰爭|皮特堡圍攻戰]]期間，英國人曾考慮利用天花對抗法國及其美洲原住民盟友。<ref name=Anderson>{{cite book|1=|title=''Crucible of War''|author=Fred Anderson|publisher=''Vitage Books''|date=2001|url=http://www.amazon.com/Crucible-War-British-America-1754-1766/dp/0375706364|access-date=2015-07-18|archive-date=2015-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722135922/http://www.amazon.com/Crucible-War-British-America-1754-1766/dp/0375706364|dead-url=no}}</ref>根據威廉·特倫特（一位當地的商人）於1763年6月24日寫下的日記，{{link-en|德拉瓦族|Lenape}}曾派遣兩位酋長要求英人停戰，臨走時英方代表給了他們取自天花醫院的兩條毯子與一個手帕。<ref name=Anderson/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.history.org/Foundation/journal/Spring04/warfare.cfm|title=Colonial Germ Warfare|author=Harold B. Gill, Jr.|work=CW Journal: Spring 04|accessdate=2015-07-18|archive-date=2015-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801092104/http://www.history.org/Foundation/journal/Spring04/warfare.cfm|dead-url=no}}</ref>至於這是不是一次官方下令的生物戰行動則不得而知，但多數歷史學家並不認為此舉能有效地散播病毒。除此，有指英國也曾在[[美國獨立戰爭|美國獨立戰爭]]中派遣已具免疫力的天花患者去感染美國軍隊。<ref name="BBC pox_weapon_01">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/worldwars/coldwar/pox_weapon_01.shtml |title=BBC – History – Silent Weapon: Smallpox and Biological Warfare |date=2011-02-17 |accessdate=2015-07-18 |work= |archive-date=2011-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710202956/http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/worldwars/coldwar/pox_weapon_01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Elizabeth A. Fenn|title="Biological Warfare in Eighteenth-Century North America: Beyond Jeffery Amherst"|work=''The Journal of American History''|volume=86, No. 4 (Mar., 2000)|page=1552–1580}}</ref>《澳洲研究雜誌》上一篇由獨立研究者撰寫的論文表示，英海軍曾於1789年嘗試使用天花病毒對付[[新南威爾斯|新南威爾斯]]的土著部落，《醫學歷史公報》也有提及這個議題。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Warren, Christopher|title="Smallpox at Sydney Cove – who, when, why?"|work=''Journal Of Australian Studies''|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/14443058.2013.849750#preview|access-date=2015-07-18|archive-date=2019-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301082512/https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/14443058.2013.849750#preview|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過，由於當時的人常將輕度天花與水痘混淆，故此生物戰是否真出現則具爭議性。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/radionational/programs/ockhamsrazor/chicken-pox-or-smallpox-in-the-colony-at-sydney/2972652#transcript|title=Chicken pox or smallpox in the colony at Sydney Cove in April, 1789|author=Brigitte Seega|date=2010-09-19|accessdate=2015-07-18|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925213836/http://www.abc.net.au/radionational/programs/ockhamsrazor/chicken-pox-or-smallpox-in-the-colony-at-sydney/2972652#transcript|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[二次世界大戰|二次世界大戰]]期間，美、英、[[731部隊|日]]三國的科學家都曾嘗試研發天花武器<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dhhr.wv.gov/oeps/disease/documents/usamriid_bluebook.pdf|format=PDF|title=USAMRIID's Medical Management of Biological Casualties Handbook|accessdate=2015-07-18|work=|archive-date=2015-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150812210729/http://www.dhhr.wv.gov/oeps/disease/Documents/USAMRIID_BlueBook.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但因考慮到疫苗的廣泛度而從沒有大規模地使用<ref name="BBC pox_weapon_02">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/worldwars/coldwar/pox_weapon_02.shtml |title=BBC – History – Silent Weapon: Smallpox and Biological Warfare |accessdate=2015-07-18 |work= |archive-date=2011-08-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/61CEruxHt?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/worldwars/coldwar/pox_weapon_01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1947年，[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]在距離莫斯科東北75公里的[[謝爾吉耶夫鎮|謝爾吉耶夫鎮]]設立了天花武器開發廠。<ref name="Alibek">{{cite book |title=Biohazard: The Chilling True Story of the Largest Covert Biological Weapons Program in the World—Told from Inside by the Man Who Ran It |url=https://archive.org/details/biohazardchillin00alib_0 |publisher=Delta |location=New York |isbn=0-385-33496-6|author1 = Alibek K|author2 = Handelman S|date=1999}}</ref>二十四年後，於[[鹹海|鹹海]]一座小島上進行的生物測試不幸發生意外，導致了天花爆發。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Enserink M |title=Biowarfare. Did bioweapons test cause a deadly smallpox outbreak? |journal=Science |volume=296 |issue=5576 |pages=2116–7 |pmid=12077372 |doi=10.1126/science.296.5576.2116|date=2002}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Bellomo|first1=Michael|last2=Zelicoff|first2=Alan P.|title=Microbe: are we ready for the next plague?|url=https://archive.org/details/microbeareweread00alan|publisher=American Management Association|location=New York|isbn=978-0-8144-0865-0|page=[https://archive.org/details/microbeareweread00alan/page/101 101]|date=2005}}</ref>在國際輿論壓力下，蘇方允許美英科學團隊視察其[[Biopreparat|生物製品部門]]的四個主要設施，雖說有關團隊最終被當地的科學家拒絕入門。<ref name= Preston>{{Cite book | last1 = Preston | first1 = Richard | title = The Demon in the Freezer | publisher = Fawcett | location = | isbn = 0-345-46663-2 | pages = 105–115 }}</ref>1992年，蘇聯生物武器專家{{link-ru|肯·阿里貝克|Алибеков, Канатжан Байзакович}}堅稱蘇方已儲存了20噸抗疫苗性的天花武器製品，亦準備了[[彈頭|彈頭]]將之散播，但此說法從沒有獲得第三方的驗證。1997年，俄國政府宣布將所有剩存的天花病毒樣本移至國家病毒與生物科技研究中心。隨著蘇聯的解體及無數前蘇聯生物武器專家失業，美國政府擔心天花武器的研究資料可能已落入恐怖分子手中。<ref name=CDCcourse>{{cite web|url=http://www.bt.cdc.gov/agent/smallpox/training/overview/pdf/eradicationhistory.pdf|title=History and Epidemiology of Global Smallpox Eradication|work="Smallpox: Disease, Prevention, and Intervention"|publisher=CDC; World Health Organization|page=16–17|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070715234749/http://www.bt.cdc.gov/agent/smallpox/training/overview/pdf/eradicationhistory.pdf|archivedate=2007-07-15|access-date=2015-07-18}}</ref>除此，也有人擔憂{{link-en|人工基因合成法|Artificial gene synthesis}}可使用[[基因組|基因組]]的電子存檔結合任何現存之痘病毒使天花病毒重新面世。<ref name=sunshine>{{cite web|url=http://www.biosafety-info.net/file_dir/413148854af122567.pdf|title=The Genetic Engineering of Smallpox|accessdate=2015-07-18|author=|date=2002|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170119/http://www.biosafety-info.net/file_dir/413148854af122567.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>因此，要求加強法律監管私藏天花病毒樣本及徹底消除所有天花病毒資料的意見此起彼落。<ref name=Synbiorisk>{{cite web|url=http://www.smallpoxbiosafety.org/papers/WHAvariola2011.pdf|title=Smallpox Virus Stocks at the 64th WHA – Implementing the Conclusions of the Major Review|accessdate=2015-07-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924102751/http://www.smallpoxbiosafety.org/papers/WHAvariola2011.pdf|archivedate=2015-09-24}}</ref>

===著名病例===
歷史上有不少名人感染天花。除了[[古埃及|古埃及]][[法老|法老]][[拉美西斯五世|拉美西斯五世]]之外<ref name="Koplow 2003">{{cite book|last=Koplow|first=David|title=Smallpox: The Fight to Eradicate a Global Scourge|url=https://archive.org/details/smallpoxfighttoe00kopl|publisher=University of California Press|location=Berkeley and Los Angeles, CA|isbn=0-520-23732-3|date=2003}}</ref>，英國女王[[伊莉莎白一世|伊莉莎白一世]]、俄羅斯皇帝[[彼得二世_(俄國)|彼得二世]]及[[彼得三世_(俄國)|彼得三世]]均為天花患者<ref name="doctorzebra.com">{{cite web|title=President Abraham Lincoln: Health & Medical History|url=http://www.doctorzebra.com/prez/g16.htm#25|date=2007-03-24|accessdate=2015-07-18|archive-date=2015-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150710025155/http://www.doctorzebra.com/prez/g16.htm#25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。雖然彼得二世最後不敵病魔，但彼得三世與其妻子卻能康復。不過，基於擔心王位繼承者[[保羅一世_(俄國)|保羅一世]]的安危，彼得三世的妻子邀請了一位蘇格蘭醫生為她及保羅進行人工接種術，並將之推廣至民間。<ref>{{cite book|author=Massie, Robert K|title=''Catherine the Great: Portrait of as Woman''|url=https://archive.org/details/catherinegreatpo00mass_3|page=[https://archive.org/details/catherinegreatpo00mass_3/page/387 387]–388|publisher=Random House|location=New York|isbn=978-0-679-45672-8|date=2011}}</ref>[[美國總統|美國總統]][[喬治·華盛頓|喬治·華盛頓]]、[[安德魯·傑克遜|安德魯·傑克遜]]及[[亞伯拉罕·林肯|亞伯拉罕·林肯]]也都患上過天花<ref name="Michael B. A. Oldstone">{{cite book|title=Viruses, Plagues, and History|url=https://archive.org/details/virusesplagueshi00mdmi|last=Oldstone|first=Michael|pages=[https://archive.org/details/virusesplagueshi00mdmi/page/65 65]–71|publisher=Oxford University Press| isbn=978-0-19-532731-1|date=2010}}</ref>：華盛頓是在到訪[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]時染病；傑克遜是在獨立戰爭時的英軍監獄中發病；而林肯則應該是從他兒子處沾染了病毒。<ref name="Michael B. A. Oldstone"/>匈牙利詩人[[克爾切伊·費倫茨|克爾切伊·費倫茨]]及[[奧地利帝國|奧地利]]音樂家[[莫扎特|莫扎特]]是曾感染天花的文藝人。<ref>{{cite book|author=Szinnyei József|url=http://mek.niif.hu/03600/03630/html/k/k12495.htm|title=Magyar írók élete és munkái|publisher=Arcanum, Budapest|isbn=963-86029-9-6|language=hu|date=2000|access-date=2015-07-18|archive-date=2014-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906191638/http://mek.niif.hu/03600/03630/html/k/k12495.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在[[亞洲|亞洲]]地區，[[中國|中國]][[清代|清代]]蒙古[[輝特部|輝特部]]首領[[阿睦爾撒納|阿睦爾撒納]]，[[順治皇帝|順治皇帝]]和[[同治皇帝|同治皇帝]]（有傳死於[[梅毒|梅毒]]）也是因染天花而死，而[[康熙皇帝|康熙皇帝]]幼年曾感染天花後痊癒 (亦是其中一個令其被選為皇位繼承人的原因)。[[日本戰國時代|日本戰國時代]]的[[大名_(稱謂)|大名]][[伊達政宗|伊達政宗]]因幼年感染天花導致右眼失明。

===宗教信仰===
“痘疹娘娘”為古代中國民間信仰中，施展天花咒語的神靈，人們避之則吉。<ref name="HopkinsDonald">{{cite book|author=Hopkins, Donald R|title=Princes and Peasants: Smallpox in History|url=https://archive.org/details/princespeasantss0000hopk|location=United States of American|publisher=''University of Chicago Press''|date=1983}}</ref><ref name="GiblinJames">{{cite book|author=Giblin, James C|title=When Plague Strikes: The Black Death, Smallpox, AIDS|url=https://archive.org/details/whenplaguestrike00gibl|location=United States of America|publisher=HarperCollins Publishers|date=1995}}</ref>[[除夕|除夕]]夜，兒童在臨睡時需配戴面具遮掩容貌，避免在夜裡引起娘娘的注意。<ref name="GiblinJames"/>若有人罹患了天花，人們會在病人的家裡放置聖壇，祈求疾病能盡快消失。若病人成功康復，他們會用紙製的椅子或船把聖壇運走，將之焚燒；若病人不幸死去，他們會對其施咒，趕走娘娘。<ref name="HopkinsDonald"/>明末崇禎年間，江西名醫[[喻昌|喻昌]]（1585-1664）在其著作《寓意草》記載[[顧諟明|顧諟明]]的次子感染天花，“其痘苗淡紅磊落，中含水色，明潤可愛，且顆粒稀疎，如晨星之麗天。”有醫生說是「狀元痘」，乃是明清痘醫看痘文化的一種說法。<ref>喻昌：《寓意草》卷4</ref>

古印度同樣有這樣的天花之神，即深受人們敬畏的“{{link-en|史塔拉|Shitala}}”。<ref name="GiblinJames" />畫像顯示，她右手執有能散播天花病毒的掃帚，左手同時拿着可舒緩病情的聖水瓶。<ref name="GiblinJames"/><ref>{{cite book|author=Wiley, Andrea S., & Allen, John S.|title=Medical Anthropology: A Biocultural Approach|location=New York|publisher=Oxford University Press|date=2009}}</ref>印度人不論健康與否都會到聖壇拜祭，祈求自己能遠離病魔。有些人為了避免天花之神入屋，會在自己的房頂擺放食物及食水，用以供奉及打發祂走。<ref>{{cite book|author=Tucker, Jonathan B.|title=Scourge: The Once and Future Threat of Smallpox|url=https://archive.org/details/scourgeoncefutur0000tuck|location=New York|publisher=Atlantic Monthly Press|date=2001}}</ref>

日本、非洲等地沒有這類受人們拜祭的天花之神，取而代之的是深受人們厭惡的[[疱瘡神|疱瘡神]]。當地人相信紅色能驅趕疱瘡神，故病患者都會用紅色物件佈置家裡。此習俗在12世紀傳到了歐洲，曾獲[[查理五世_(法蘭西)|-{zh:法皇查理五世; zh-hans:法王查理五世; zh-tw:法王查理五世;zh-hk:法皇查理五世;}-]]及[[伊麗莎白一世_(英格蘭)|-{zh:英皇伊利沙伯一世; zh-hans:英王伊丽莎白一世; zh-tw:英王伊莉莎白一世;zh-hk:英皇伊利沙伯一世;}-]]採用。<ref name=SmaPoHist/>

